name: Bejibun
description: Bejibun is a typescript framework using Bun runtime with MVC (Model-View-Controller) architecture. It is designed for backend use with built-in migrations, seeders, cors, and caching systems. It also comes with command tools like scaffolding for controller, middleware, migration, model, seeder, validator, etc. And includes command for maintenance mode, allowing for application live or under maintenance.
